<p>Vimium is a Google Chrome extension which provides keyboard shortcuts for navigation and control in the spirit of the Vim editor. Watch this video to get a feel for how it works:</p>

<h1 id="features">Features</h1>

<ul>
  <li>Helps you navigate the web without touching the mouse.</li>
  <li>Uses a clever highlighting method to navigate using links.</li>
  <li>Customizable keyboard shortcuts</li>
  <li>Has an in-page help dialog to remind you of your personalized shortcuts.</li>
</ul>

